snippet.title: Best VGM 1262 - Castlevania II - Dwelling of Doom
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 236 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tiwsAs6WVyQ
Best VGM 340 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rhbGqHurV5I

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Castlevania II: Simon's Quest (1988)
Dwelling of Doom
Kenichi Matsubara
